<p>Dreaming of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ظهور-البثور-على-الوجه-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=1293" > pimples appearing on the face </a> indicates victory and kindness, and other interpretations will be explained for single women, married women, pregnant women, divorced women, and men, such as seeing <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-اللون-الأحمر-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=1058" > the color red </a>. The appearance of pimples on the face, thigh, lips, or body, or seeing pimples on the chest, or the appearance of black pimples on the hand, or pink pimples on the shoulder or leg, or seeing blackheads by Ibn. Sirin and more in the continuation of the topic:</p>
<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-ظهور-البثور-على-الوجه-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=1293" > pimples appearing on the face </a> in a dream</span></h2>
<p>Whoever sees pimples on his face in a dream, it shows the worries that the dreamer will face and will leave after a short period, while whoever sees something unnatural on his face indicates a deficiency in some religious matters, such as not praying or combining tasks, and whether the pimples contain pus.  It indicates an increase in money</p>
<p>The honorable sheikh and scholar Muhammad ibn Sirin mentioned in the chapter of diseases, disabilities, diseases, and pains, chapter 25, and he said in interpreting the vision of pimples and pimples in a dream, or interpreting the vision of red spots, despite the disgust and anxiety of most people. People from the appearance and vision of pimples and pimples, but the scholars and commentators unanimously agreed that pimples in a dream are good and victory, especially if a person sees in his dream that these pimples filled them and blood or pus came out of them, as it also indicates <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money </a> and wealth.<br/>Whoever sees red pimples on the face will propose to marry her if she is not married, or she will be affected by envy or the evil eye or be affected by envy after giving birth if she is married.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
