</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>And whoever saw pimples on the neck or face, or his clothes were defiled, then this indicates worries, debts, and bad talk, and the appearance of pimples and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-البثور-على-الوجه?page=1729" > pimples on the face </a> indicates a lack of religion, such as leaving prayer.</p>
<p>As for whoever dreams of the appearance of many sores and pimples on his body, he will get a lot of money according to the quantity and duration.</p>
<p>Seeing pimples and <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-البثور-على-الجسم?page=3201" > pimples on the body </a> in a dream contains some good indications for the fortune teller, and among these indications is that it indicates that a person will get <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money </a>, especially if he dreams that he has scabies, smallpox, sores. Or general pimples.  Some saw that the pimples on the body in a dream indicate a person's victory over others.</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
