</script></div></div><div class="clear"></div>
<p><span></span></p>
<p>Whoever saw these pimples on the body in a dream, it has a bad meaning for the dreamer, and among these indications is that the person is drowning in a swamp of worries, especially if this person sees the pimples on his face.<br/>If a person sees pimples on his body in a dream and a bad smell comes out of these pimples, this is evidence that he carries debts and worries, and even people humiliate him in honor of his offer because they are angry with him.  for him.</p>
<p>Seeing <strong>a lot of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-البثور-على-الوجه?page=1729" > pimples on the face </a> in a dream</strong>, this vision shows the thinker's deficiency in prayer and with great regret, and this vision warns you and alerts you or alerts you that you are a backward person in your prayer or worship in general.<br/>Seeing seeds in abundance on the body in a dream indicates financial crises and it is said that it indicates the existence of a large number of debts.  But there is a difference between crises, as there may be crises in his life, and most of us suffer from crises, but this vision may mean for some people an accumulation of debts on them.<br/><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحبوب-في-المنام?page=2906" > <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-الحب-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3685" > Seeing love </a>and </a> on the body and the pimples bleed in a dream, and this vision is one of the praiseworthy visions, indicating the acquisition of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الكثير-من-المال-لابن-سيرين?page=1849" > a lot of money </a> in the future, God willing.<br/>Seeing your loved ones with beads full of pus and pus and their foul smell in a dream indicates that people hate him and with great sorrow, meaning that this vision shows that people do not love you and do not tolerate you and do not tolerate you.  I love to deal with you.<br/>Seeing <strong>pink pimples in a dream</strong> for the unmarried, marriage, that is, if an unmarried girl sees pink pimples on her body or face, this indicates her marriage, as well as for an unmarried young man.<br/>As for <strong>coffee beans in a dream</strong>, if it is in the body, it indicates excellence and success for singles and work for married people.<br/>As for the structure of married people, it indicates the existence of a job or the opening of a new work opportunity for them.<br/>Pink pimples appear in a married woman's dream, showing mutual love between her and her husband.<br/><strong><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الفاصوليا-السوداء?page=3593" > Black beans </a> in a dream</strong>, and this vision for a married woman indicates providing care for her husband, and for divorced and widowed women, her livelihood, God willing, may He be exalted.<br/>Seeing many different pimples in a dream can be pink, brown, and black.  This vision indicates the pregnancy of a married woman, and different pimples in a dream about <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > pregnant women </a> indicate that the child will be a girl, God willing.<br/>But some scholars who interpret dreams said that the pimples that indicate that the child is a girl are pink pimples, while brown and black pimples indicate that the child will be a male.<br/>Meaning pregnant when she sees pink pimples, this means that the child is a girl.<br/>Pregnant, when she sees brown or black pimples, the <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-طفل-ذكر-لابن-سيرين?page=627" > child is a male </a>.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of pimples and spots in a dream for a single woman</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-فتاة-في-المنام?page=4046" > Seeing a girl </a> who is not married or a single woman with the appearance of pimples, pimples or brown or red spots on her body and skin, predicts her engagement or engagement or marriage if she is of marriageable age, or her promotion at work or her success in her studies.  For a single woman, the spread of pink pimples or their appearance on a part of her body indicates that <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-شخص-ما-في-المنام?page=2395" > someone </a> is impressed by her and generally describes her as good news for happy and joyful news or good luck and success</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
