<p><span></span></p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of pimples and spots in a dream for a married woman</span></h2>
<p>As for <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-رؤية-المرأة-في-المنام-لابن-سيرين?page=3591" > seeing a woman </a> who is married, the spread of pimples and spots on her body in a dream is an indicator of her husband's love for her and his good appearance to her, even if he is in his sixties.  Pimples in a married woman's dream are a sign of money, livelihood, and profit, whether it is the married woman herself or her husband, especially seeing blackheads because they are a sign of money and livelihood.</p>
<p>The best vision for a married woman is to dream of pimples and pimples spreading on her face, hands, or feet, as this indicates safety and reassurance in terms of livelihood and money, or in terms of work.  It indicates a relationship of <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-الحب-والاحترام?page=2119" > love and respect </a> that brings the couple together, or that it is a harbinger of healing for the sick, and the best vision is to see large pimples (pimples) from which pus or pus or blood comes out, such a vision portends the disappearance of worries, problems, and pains, especially if the substance that comes out of these pimples is black in color.</p>
<h2><span>Interpretation of pimples and spots in a dream for a pregnant woman</span></h2>
<p><a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > A pregnant woman </a> who sees pimples or spots in her dream, especially the appearance of these pimples on her face, is an indicator of the health and safety of the fetus in her womb, while <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> who sees pimples or spots in different parts. of the body is a reflection of her health, safety, and self-care, and whenever <a href="https://gptafser.com/post/تفسير-حلم-المرأة-الحامل-لابن-سيرين?page=691" > a pregnant woman </a> sees in her dream that the pimples …</p><div class="angwp_84394 _ning_cont _ning_hidden _ning_outer _align_center responsive" data-aid="0" data-bid="84394" data-size="custom" style="max-width:100%; width:100%;height:inherit;"><div class="_ning_label _left" style=""></div><div class="_ning_inner" style=""><script type="text/javascript">
